<h2>About Us</h2>
<p>Two Scoop Games is Alex Bezuska and Eric Lathrop. Based out of Louisville, Kentucky, Two Scoop Games has produced several games for various game jams while honing their craft. Web developers by trade, Two Scoop Games build games for the web with a mission of advancing the number of cross-platform games native to the web. Two Scoop Games is an active participant in <a href="http://gamedevlou.org">Game Dev Lou</a>, Louisville's local game development group.</p>

